{"tid":2217479,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【會師中環】滙控死因是用完即棄 - 神仙丁","createTime":"2020-09-25T12:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T13:41:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"919e8c41896491a1bfd21248a0255e8e06b30eeb","tid":2217479,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200925/TFA3TSDSH5CXDHCS4DSCR65SZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200925%2FTFA3TSDSH5CXDHCS4DSCR65SZU%2F&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzpBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=a5332589\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200925%2FTFA3TSDSH5CXDHCS4DSCR65SZU%2F&h=0fb83ff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200925/TFA3TSDSH5CXDHCS4DSCR65SZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【會師中環】滙控死因是用完即棄 - 神仙丁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RGP-wOsMlbFVEU4DtjRpk8ApFEc=/5661x3844/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FKO4PVWF4JD5FLFWA2BQ76J4BU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRGP-wOsMlbFVEU4DtjRpk8ApFEc%3D%2F5661x3844%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFKO4PVWF4JD5FLFWA2BQ76J4BU.jpg&h=1da98b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■滙控不是根正苗紅，再親都親不過中國四大行，利用價值自然低落。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n滙豐控股（005）跌穿世紀供股價28元，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，我相信除此之外，大貓的終極死因還是「用完即棄」，這亦是中國歷史的傳統：過橋抽板、鳥盡弓藏、兔死狗烹。看李嘉誠就知這種傳統做法從沒有消失。超人多年來不知捐了多少錢、投資了多少資金返大陸，對大陸經濟發展貢獻巨大，現在又不是被批鬥成賣國商人？如果超人不是一早睇穿其本質、及早撤資，現在只會是另一間滙控。<br />\n<br />\n以故知今，就算滙控一開始就向中國靠攏，我相信到最後亦是同一個結局。始終滙控不是根正苗紅，再親都親不過中國四大行，而且四大銀行已養到牛高馬大，滙控的利用價值就更見低落，那為何還要保留？滙控的命運早已寫好，大貓注定被中資打擊，被人收購相信已是最好下場，而企錯邊只是令其早死一點罷了。<br />\n<br />\n神仙丁<br />\n<br />\n《審計搵丁》負責人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://facebook.com/AuditSlave/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com